      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. While it currently runs, the engine requires significant mechanical attention, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. The exterior has substantial body damage and rust, and the interior shows heavy wear and tear, including several non-functional electronics. This car would be best suited as a project vehicle or for parts, as it will likely need a major overhaul to be reliable for daily use.",
