    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, while the interior is pristine, showing zero signs of wear on the premium upholstery. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine runs silently and powerful, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and every electronic feature functions exactly as intended. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who expects the highest standard of quality and performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
